snippet: President Petro O. Poroshenko has ordered the military to send reinforcements to Ukraine’s east.
abstract: Ukraine's Pres Petro O Poroshenko orders military to send reinforcements to eastern Ukraine in response to elections held in rebel-controlled areas; Ukraine, European Union and the United States have said that elections violated peace agreement.
lead_paragraph: President Petro O. Poroshenko has ordered the military to send reinforcements to Ukraine’s east.

headline.main: Ukraine: President Orders Forces Bolstered in the Separatist East
headline.print_headline: Ukraine: President Orders Forces Bolstered in the Separatist East
